Re: Otaku?
by Harisenbon » Wed 09.24.2008 11:40 pm Think about it this way:Some people like being called a geek.Some people call themselves geeks.Some people would hate being called a geek.It's the same thing. Otaku is the word for geek. How people respond to it completely depends on the person in question.
