Re: Otaku?
by MMM » Tue 09.30.2008 12:01 pm two_heads_talking wrote:Isn't the term Otakusama one that can be used in the business world to mean you?Not only the business world (and I don't think you hear it with sama so much, but that's possible) but お宅 is a very polite way of referring to you or your home or family.This term was then adopted to refer to uber-nerds because of how polite they spoke to each other.あら！あの子、お宅のルーシーちゃんに砂投げたわよ！Oh, look! That kid threw sand at your child, Lucy!
